# Water dimer, PBE0 with the CD-derived automatic auxiliary basis (RI).
# Exercises FittingBasis Auto (cholesky_aux_basis + FittingLmaxInc pruning)
# with exact exchange -- the path enabled by the Auto/AutoABS split.
System water_dimer.xyz
Method hyb_gga_xc_pbeh
Basis aug-cc-pVDZ
Direct false
IntegralThresh 1e-14
JKMethod RI
FittingBasis Auto

Logfile water_dimer_pbe0_cdaux.log
SaveChk water_dimer_pbe0_cdaux.chk
BasisRotate false
DFTGrid 50 -194
